The Olympic flame does not illuminate every event.
Further from the center, partly in the shade are the sports that are not generally recognized: air pistol shooting, archery, badminton, taekwondo.
We will always have the breast swimming and we will reign for a long time.
But if I am humbly allowed to make arguments for my particular darling, then let me draw attention to the discreet charm of the trampoline.
